Installation instructions
=========================

Easy Install:

    https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/cgjalgdhmbpaacnnejmodfinclbdgaci


Developer Install:

    git clone http://github.com/matheeeny/Syntaxtic.git

    Open chrome extension manager: Window -> Extensions

    Click on "Developer mode" to show the "Load unpacked extension..." button

    Click "Load unpacked extension..."

    Open the 'Syntaxtic' folder you cloned


http://code.google.com/chrome/extensions/getstarted.html#load
